title: Railworks TS2015 AP Class 47 Sound Pack (Pro)
description:
As requested, updated sound pack. Liverpool to Manchester support. 15.09.2014

During the installation process, these sounds will be applied to all default liveries (BR Green/Blue/Large Logo, InterCity Swallow, Rail Express & Triple Grey) contained within the RS.com European Community Asset Pack and also the class 47 included with the RS.com Liverpool to Manchester & RS.com West Somerset Railway routes. As well as this, an EasyApply utility is included which means that with a few clicks, you can apply these sounds to other reskins of the class 47 (RS.com European Community Asset Pack only).



Please support the developers and buy some of their content if you can afford it.


If you would like to contribute, please read the Readme.pdf.


A Team tpb_4_ever upload
